164
00:09:51,007 --> 00:09:53,760
[NAUD] Okay, this will be
the very last fight

165
00:09:53,802 --> 00:09:56,596
of the Baels versus
the Gremorys Rating Game!

166
00:09:56,638 --> 00:09:58,973
