from the Red Dragon Emperor.

184
00:10:36,177 --> 00:10:37,428
Let's see your true power!

185
00:10:37,470 --> 00:10:39,305
[ISSEI]
Prepare to die!

186
00:10:41,558 --> 00:10:44,227
[ISSEI shouts]

187
00:10:46,104 --> 00:10:49,065
[BOTH grunt]

188
00:10:49,107 --> 00:10:51,526
[ISSEI] Eff this shit!
Am I right, Ddraig?

189
00:10:51,568 --> 00:10:53,903
[DDRAIG] Yes!
Boost! Boost! Boost! Boost!

190
00:10:53,945 --> 00:10:57,365
