has transformed

201
00:11:36,237 --> 00:11:38,823
‐into a giant golden lion!
‐[AZAZEL] It can't be.

202
00:11:38,865 --> 00:11:40,950
‐The Lion of Nemea?
‐[NAUD] What's that?

203
00:11:40,992 --> 00:11:42,702
Specifically, it was
the Lion that fought

204
00:11:42,744 --> 00:11:44,871
against Heracles
in ancient mythology.

205
00:11:44,913 --> 00:11:46,623
Not long
after the ferocious battle,

206
00:11:46,664 --> 00:11:48,374
it was sealed
into a Sacred Gear,

207
00:11:48,416 --> 00:11:51,377
and became one of the thirteen
legendary Longinus.

208
00:11:51,419 --> 00:11:53,379
The weapon was rumored
to be strong enough

209
00:11:53,421 --> 00:11:55,757
to crack the earth
with a single swing.

210
00:11:55,798 --> 00:11:57,383
A battle axe
that could transform

211
00:11:57,425 --> 00:12:00,094
into a giant lion,
Regulus Nemea!

212
00:12:00,136 --> 00:12:01,971
What's odd is
that I'd heard its master

213
00:12:02,013 --> 00:12:04,182
had been MIA
for quite some time.

214
00:12:04,224 --> 00:12:05,391
That's correct.

215
00:12:05,433 --> 00:12:07,018
His master was murdered.

216
00:12:07,060 --> 00:12:09,687
When I found him, it was clear
there'd been a struggle.

217
00:12:09,729 --> 00:12:11,689
The group that attacked him
was still there.

218
00:12:11,731 --> 00:12:14,275
But the battle axe
had turned into a lion

219
00:12:14,317 --> 00:12:16,152
and destroyed
every last one of 'em.

220
00:12:16,194 --> 00:12:19,030
That's when I decided
to make him part of my family.

221
00:12:19,072 --> 00:12:21,157
How's that for a backstory?

222
00:12:21,199 --> 00:12:23,117
So, it's an intelligent
Longinus

223
00:12:23,159 --> 00:12:25,161
