why you never sent out

229
00:12:37,006 --> 00:12:38,466
your pawn until the end.

230
00:12:38,508 --> 00:12:40,593
[ISSEI] Prez, take care
of the giant pussy!

231
00:12:40,635 --> 00:12:43,137
