it seems slower, too.

240
00:13:26,389 --> 00:13:28,933
We won't die easily.

241
00:13:28,975 --> 00:13:30,810
Don't worry, Sairaorg,
we'll send you

242
00:13:30,852 --> 00:13:32,979
to the Red Dragon Emperor
in the best of states.

243
00:13:33,021 --> 00:13:36,941
[gasps] Thanks, Kiba.
You guys really did me a solid!

244
00:13:36,983 --> 00:13:39,485
